summary: This document appears to be a lieutenant's log and daily activity log from the Bureau of Prisons for Saturday, August 10, 2019. The date is significant as it is the day Jeffrey Epstein was found dead in his jail cell at the Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York.

events.title: Daily Activity Log Entry
events.description: Lieutenant's log and daily activity log for the Bureau of Prisons was recorded.

keyFacts: The document is a lieutenant's log and daily activity log dated August 10, 2019.
August 10, 2019, is the date Jeffrey Epstein was found deceased in his jail cell.
The log originates from the Bureau of Prisons, the agency responsible for Epstein's custody.
